1
00:00:08,436 --> 00:00:20,436
Officail Website : dramacool.club  Translate by =Qari= @Team Viki

2
00:00:10,460 --> 00:00:13,340
♪ I drift across the boundless skies ♪

3
00:00:14,020 --> 00:00:16,900
♪ Through deserts where no one goes ♪

4
00:00:17,020 --> 00:00:18,900
♪ Seeking myself ♪

5
00:00:18,980 --> 00:00:20,860
♪ The self I long to find ♪

6
00:00:24,020 --> 00:00:26,900
♪ Lost in a maze of lies ♪

7
00:00:27,500 --> 00:00:30,380
♪ I break into your sea of clouds ♪

8
00:00:30,540 --> 00:00:32,860
♪ It traps me ♪

9
00:00:32,900 --> 00:00:35,380
♪ It redeems me ♪

10
00:00:37,580 --> 00:00:43,020
♪ Which hue of the sky is your love? ♪

11
00:00:44,460 --> 00:00:46,740
♪ Or is it the burning flame ♪

12
00:00:46,820 --> 00:00:51,860
♪ Found only in storms? ♪

13
00:00:55,380 --> 00:01:00,020
♪ You are the mark engraved upon my heart ♪

14
00:01:02,300 --> 00:01:08,380
♪ From then on all my
memories tremble for you ♪

15
00:01:08,660 --> 00:01:11,380
♪ What I cannot forget
is that fleeting gaze ♪

16
00:01:12,140 --> 00:01:14,820
♪ What I cannot escape
is passion born in chaos ♪

17
00:01:15,700 --> 00:01:17,140
♪ How I long to hold you again ♪

18
00:01:17,500 --> 00:01:19,020
♪ How I long to hold you again ♪

19
00:01:19,260 --> 00:01:22,020
♪ Our love, high among the clouds ♪

20
00:01:22,140 --> 00:01:24,780
♪ Is sealed with that kiss ♪

21
00:01:25,980 --> 00:01:27,956
[Love in The Clouds]

22
00:01:27,980 --> 00:01:29,996
[Adapted from Bai Lu Cheng
Shuang's "Love in The Clouds"]

23
00:01:30,020 --> 00:01:33,020
[Episode 30]

24
00:01:34,350 --> 00:01:36,150
Spiritual power from
Zhushui Spiritual State?

25
00:01:36,560 --> 00:01:38,240
Did the Emperor of Zhushui give it to you?

26
00:01:38,590 --> 00:01:40,980
No wonder your power
surged at the tea gathering.

27
00:01:42,840 --> 00:01:43,930
Who are you taking me to?

28
00:01:44,280 --> 00:01:45,460
The Emperor of Zhushui?

29
00:01:45,790 --> 00:01:47,490
So you were faking it all along!

30
00:01:50,430 --> 00:01:52,380
The black lingzhi mushroom
can revive your cat.

31
00:01:54,560 --> 00:01:56,040
I'm sure Ming Xin knows that already.

32
00:01:56,230 --> 00:01:57,350
Do you intend to play along?

33
00:01:58,870 --> 00:02:00,046
Is there anything else

34
00:02:00,070 --> 00:02:01,770
in my mind that you can't read?

35
00:02:02,150 --> 00:02:04,210
Right, Warrior Goddess.

36
00:02:04,430 --> 00:02:06,100
Everything is within your calculations.

37
00:02:07,680 --> 00:02:09,170
Ming Xin will show himself.

38
00:02:09,400 --> 00:02:11,010
I want to settle the score with him

39
00:02:11,310 --> 00:02:12,376
and might as well use the opportunity

40
00:02:12,400 --> 00:02:14,240
to get the last piece
of the Recording Mirror.

41
00:02:18,680 --> 00:02:20,280
Do you dare return to Yaoguang Mountain?

42
00:02:20,520 --> 00:02:22,380
What if Father punishes you?

43
00:02:22,870 --> 00:02:23,870
Punish me?

44
00:02:23,960 --> 00:02:25,200
Why should I be afraid of that?

45
00:02:25,960 --> 00:02:27,890
When I reveal the truth to everyone,

46
00:02:28,360 --> 00:02:30,540
who should be afraid? You or me?

47
00:02:31,360 --> 00:02:34,170
Now that you've fallen for the trap

48
00:02:34,590 --> 00:02:36,730
let's settle our score once and for all.

49
00:02:40,280 --> 00:02:42,170
Open your eyes and see

50
00:02:42,590 --> 00:02:43,590
what I have here.

51
00:02:45,840 --> 00:02:46,840
How can this be?

52
00:02:47,960 --> 00:02:50,220
Mu Qibai has half of the Recording Mirror.

53
00:02:50,710 --> 00:02:52,570
How did you get the one in my possession

54
00:02:53,280 --> 00:02:54,610
that went missing?

55
00:03:54,630 --> 00:03:55,630
Impossible.

56
00:03:56,080 --> 00:03:57,450
You have the Heavenly Grief.

57
00:03:58,000 --> 00:03:59,000
How can you...

58
00:04:06,150 --> 00:04:07,260
The Recording Mirror

59
00:04:08,030 --> 00:04:10,500
will prove that you poisoned
me with the Heavenly Grief

60
00:04:10,710 --> 00:04:12,500
and colluded with the Emperor of Zhushui.

61
00:04:12,710 --> 00:04:14,780
How do you think Yaoguang
Palace will punish you?

62
00:04:15,470 --> 00:04:17,540
Your punishment will be more important

63
00:04:17,870 --> 00:04:18,870
than my identity.

64
00:04:19,510 --> 00:04:20,900
I hate

65
00:04:21,430 --> 00:04:24,580
that I didn't kill you back
then in Jixing Abyss when I had

66
00:04:25,190 --> 00:04:27,810
the Blood Moon Ring that
could catalyze the netherbeasts!

67
00:04:29,630 --> 00:04:31,370
Do you have any idea what you did?

68
00:04:32,480 --> 00:04:34,846
You poisoned me so that
you can be the crown prince.

69
00:04:34,870 --> 00:04:35,980
That's a personal agenda.

70
00:04:36,830 --> 00:04:38,046
But letting the netherbeasts out

71
00:04:38,070 --> 00:04:39,216
will only bring suffering
to the Six Realms!

72
00:04:39,240 --> 00:04:40,980
You're the greatest fool ever!

73
00:04:48,000 --> 00:04:49,100
So what?

74
00:04:50,000 --> 00:04:51,000
Ming Xian.

75
00:04:51,480 --> 00:04:52,490
Were you the one

76
00:04:53,040 --> 00:04:55,846
who sealed the netherbeast army

77
00:04:55,870 --> 00:04:56,930
alongside Ji Bozai?

78
00:04:57,600 --> 00:05:00,020
Ji Bozai and you fell in love?

79
00:05:02,310 --> 00:05:03,780
How preposterous.

80
00:05:04,270 --> 00:05:06,930
You ruined the plan of
the Emperor of Zhushui.

81
00:05:07,310 --> 00:05:08,310
Do you think

82
00:05:08,750 --> 00:05:10,780
he will let you go?

83
00:05:14,190 --> 00:05:15,710
Your right hand is your dominant hand.

84
00:05:16,190 --> 00:05:17,190
Therefore,

85
00:05:17,510 --> 00:05:20,170
you poisoned me with your right hand.

86
00:05:20,360 --> 00:05:21,810
Ming Xian, what are you doing?

87
00:05:21,950 --> 00:05:23,370
No!

88
00:05:34,120 --> 00:05:35,120
Ming Xin.

89
00:05:35,240 --> 00:05:36,540
You poisoned me.

90
00:05:36,750 --> 00:05:39,286
Because of that, my spiritual
veins were damaged and I lost

91
00:05:39,310 --> 00:05:40,310
in the tournament.

92
00:05:41,040 --> 00:05:42,410
To fulfill your selfish desire,

93
00:05:42,630 --> 00:05:44,310
you forsook your duty to Yaoguang Mountain

94
00:05:47,950 --> 00:05:50,020
and colluded with Zhushui Spiritual State.

95
00:05:50,240 --> 00:05:51,410
You summoned the blood moon

96
00:05:51,800 --> 00:05:54,040
and attempted to destroy
Jixing Abyss with netherbeasts.

97
00:06:00,870 --> 00:06:01,870
Today,

98
00:06:01,950 --> 00:06:03,430
I shall take away all your dexterity.

99
00:06:04,360 --> 00:06:05,660
An eye

100
00:06:06,360 --> 00:06:07,726
for an eye.

101
00:06:07,750 --> 00:06:08,750
Impossible.

102
00:06:10,070 --> 00:06:11,700
Mu Qibai told me

103
00:06:13,360 --> 00:06:15,920
that only the Golden Millet Dream
could cure the Heavenly Grief.

104
00:06:16,870 --> 00:06:18,930
You can use your
spiritual veins at will now,

105
00:06:20,190 --> 00:06:21,930
which means you are cured.

106
00:06:23,870 --> 00:06:27,140
Did Ji Bozai truly have
the Golden Millet Dream

107
00:06:28,310 --> 00:06:29,660
and give it to you?

108
00:07:20,380 --> 00:07:23,140
[Diwu Tree Root]

109
00:07:39,360 --> 00:07:40,360
My Lord.

110
00:07:41,070 --> 00:07:42,166
Considering the two hundred or so

111
00:07:42,190 --> 00:07:44,350
wandering spirits given by
Yaoguang Mountain recently,

112
00:07:44,870 --> 00:07:46,140
you will soon master

113
00:07:46,430 --> 00:07:48,846
the secret technique of Zhushui,

114
00:07:48,870 --> 00:07:50,230
the art of illusory assassination.

115
00:07:52,160 --> 00:07:53,160
Fuyue,

116
00:07:55,600 --> 00:07:57,660
I once told you many times

117
00:07:59,310 --> 00:08:01,490
that I would never become
like my father or brothers.

118
00:08:03,630 --> 00:08:04,630
You then asked

119
00:08:05,600 --> 00:08:07,170
if it was a promise to you

120
00:08:08,630 --> 00:08:10,220
or to myself.

121
00:08:13,680 --> 00:08:15,610
But I have seen the truth now.

122
00:08:18,600 --> 00:08:21,020
The blood of Zhushui flows within us.

123
00:08:22,390 --> 00:08:23,730
Are we all that different?

124
00:08:26,310 --> 00:08:29,980
We all worship the deities
of Zhushui Spiritual State.

125
00:08:32,600 --> 00:08:34,460
Perhaps we were all cursed from the start.

126
00:08:35,440 --> 00:08:36,890
Only by sacrificing our souls

127
00:08:40,270 --> 00:08:42,010
can we attain true heights.

128
00:08:44,120 --> 00:08:46,100
If that is the price

129
00:08:46,440 --> 00:08:47,890
to rise above all,

130
00:08:47,960 --> 00:08:49,250
so be it.

131
00:08:55,150 --> 00:08:56,150
My Lord.

132
00:08:57,120 --> 00:08:59,020
Whatever you have become,

133
00:08:59,230 --> 00:09:00,450
you are still you.

134
00:09:01,160 --> 00:09:04,010
I will always stay by your side.

135
00:09:37,960 --> 00:09:39,100
I couldn't defeat her

136
00:09:40,030 --> 00:09:41,650
and she even broke one of my arms.

137
00:09:43,360 --> 00:09:45,010
My bone won't ever heal again.

138
00:09:48,550 --> 00:09:49,550
The Recording Mirror...

139
00:09:50,360 --> 00:09:51,360
Wait.

140
00:09:52,360 --> 00:09:55,420
I must talk to Father before she does.

141
00:10:15,270 --> 00:10:16,850
The tea gathering isn't over.

142
00:10:17,120 --> 00:10:18,130
Why are you back so soon?

143
00:10:20,200 --> 00:10:21,420
Father, I rushed back

144
00:10:22,080 --> 00:10:26,300
because there's something affecting
the name of Yaoguang Mountain

145
00:10:27,030 --> 00:10:28,300
that you must know.

146
00:10:30,390 --> 00:10:31,390
Whatever

147
00:10:31,790 --> 00:10:33,820
could tarnish our reputation?

148
00:10:34,320 --> 00:10:35,320
Tell me.

149
00:10:39,480 --> 00:10:40,480
All of you are dismissed.

150
00:10:40,960 --> 00:10:41,960
Yes, Your Majesty.

151
00:10:52,240 --> 00:10:53,280
What happened to your arm?

152
00:11:18,630 --> 00:11:21,370
I met Ming Xian during the tea gathering.

153
00:11:21,600 --> 00:11:24,940
He broke my arm.

154
00:11:26,270 --> 00:11:27,270
Ming Xian?

155
00:11:28,480 --> 00:11:29,480
He's still alive?

156
00:11:29,630 --> 00:11:30,940
Not only is he alive,

157
00:11:32,240 --> 00:11:33,800
but he also betrayed Yaoguang Mountain,

158
00:11:34,670 --> 00:11:36,460
and sided with Jixing Abyss.

159
00:11:41,030 --> 00:11:42,250
Are you sure?

160
00:11:42,630 --> 00:11:43,850
Absolutely.

161
00:11:44,270 --> 00:11:45,610
I speak the truth.

162
00:11:46,480 --> 00:11:47,480
Moreover,

163
00:11:48,360 --> 00:11:51,060
I found something even more terrifying.

164
00:11:52,360 --> 00:11:53,360
Ming Xian

165
00:11:55,000 --> 00:11:56,340
is a girl.

166
00:11:57,840 --> 00:11:58,840
What do you mean?

167
00:11:59,870 --> 00:12:01,420
I could hardly believe it at first

168
00:12:02,000 --> 00:12:06,530
because it was just ridiculous.

169
00:12:08,630 --> 00:12:11,700
But I saw it with my own eyes.

170
00:12:11,870 --> 00:12:13,550
The warriors with me can attest to it too.

171
00:12:14,360 --> 00:12:17,180
Ming Xian is a girl.

172
00:12:18,150 --> 00:12:19,300
She got a new name, Ming Yi,

173
00:12:19,790 --> 00:12:20,940
and married Ji Bozai.

174
00:12:22,360 --> 00:12:27,010
The so-called respected
Empress must have told this lie

175
00:12:27,550 --> 00:12:28,820
to secure her position.

176
00:12:29,600 --> 00:12:31,730
She told everyone she
had given birth to a son.

177
00:12:33,000 --> 00:12:34,890
Then, she had her
daughter disguised as a man

178
00:12:38,200 --> 00:12:41,890
and deceived Yaoguang
Mountain for 21 years.

179
00:12:43,360 --> 00:12:44,420
Impossible.

180
00:12:45,870 --> 00:12:47,650
He is my son.

181
00:12:49,000 --> 00:12:50,340
He is not a girl.

182
00:12:51,000 --> 00:12:51,766
I do not know

183
00:12:51,790 --> 00:12:53,530
what evil trick the Empress used.

184
00:12:54,200 --> 00:12:57,100
But Ming Xian worked with the rival realm

185
00:12:57,360 --> 00:12:59,296
and lost on purpose during
the Qingyun Tournament.

186
00:12:59,320 --> 00:13:01,940
We then became one of the lower realms.

187
00:13:02,670 --> 00:13:04,060
This is the truth.

188
00:13:08,440 --> 00:13:09,440
I see.

189
00:13:10,910 --> 00:13:12,250
I shall investigate thoroughly.

190
00:13:13,790 --> 00:13:17,010
If Jing Shu truly
committed such an atrocity,

191
00:13:18,750 --> 00:13:22,250
I would revoke her title as the Empress.

192
00:13:26,390 --> 00:13:27,550
I have one more favor to ask.

193
00:13:28,120 --> 00:13:29,420
Father, after the tea gathering,

194
00:13:29,840 --> 00:13:31,646
please hold the Crown
Prince Conferment Ceremony

195
00:13:31,670 --> 00:13:33,180
and appoint me as the crown prince.

196
00:13:37,960 --> 00:13:39,700
His Majesty said yes?

197
00:13:40,550 --> 00:13:42,710
The conferment ceremony
will be held after three days.

198
00:13:43,600 --> 00:13:44,600
Then,

199
00:13:45,030 --> 00:13:47,340
I'll be the official crown
prince of Yaoguang Mountain.

200
00:13:49,390 --> 00:13:51,610
Great.

201
00:13:52,080 --> 00:13:53,080
Great!

202
00:13:53,120 --> 00:13:54,120
Xin.

203
00:13:57,600 --> 00:13:59,850
Why do you look so worried?

204
00:14:02,510 --> 00:14:03,510
Mother.

205
00:14:04,390 --> 00:14:06,370
There's one more problem.

206
00:14:09,720 --> 00:14:11,770
I procured the Heavenly
Grief from Mu Qibai.

207
00:14:13,240 --> 00:14:16,300
He recorded everything
with the Recording Mirror.

208
00:14:17,550 --> 00:14:18,550
And the mirror

209
00:14:21,910 --> 00:14:23,130
is in Ming Xian's possession.

210
00:14:23,670 --> 00:14:24,670
What?

211
00:14:24,790 --> 00:14:25,416
Then...

212
00:14:25,440 --> 00:14:28,010
Then you should get
the mirror back from her.

213
00:14:28,750 --> 00:14:31,300
But Ming Xian somehow
got back her spiritual veins.

214
00:14:31,750 --> 00:14:33,250
She's too strong for me.

215
00:14:37,010 --> 00:14:38,490
But the Emperor of Zhushui

216
00:14:39,930 --> 00:14:43,820
suspects Ming Xian of being
the descendant of the Bo clan.

217
00:14:45,440 --> 00:14:48,400
He asked me to capture her alive
and bring her to Zhushui Spiritual State.

218
00:14:49,240 --> 00:14:51,180
Assuming he is right,

219
00:14:53,240 --> 00:14:54,240
then Ming Yi

220
00:14:55,120 --> 00:14:59,130
does not carry the bloodline
of Yaoguang Palace.

221
00:15:17,980 --> 00:15:19,096
[Bo's Medical Classics]

222
00:15:19,120 --> 00:15:21,530
Spiritual veins destroyed
by the Heavenly Grief

223
00:15:21,600 --> 00:15:23,816
may only be restored by planting
the Golden Millet Dream in the victim.

224
00:15:23,840 --> 00:15:27,010
There is no other alternative.

225
00:15:31,840 --> 00:15:33,730
The Heavenly Grief in
me suddenly went away.

226
00:15:36,270 --> 00:15:37,430
The only possible explanation

227
00:15:38,750 --> 00:15:39,820
is that you gave it to me.

228
00:15:41,790 --> 00:15:43,420
But I had no idea at all.

229
00:15:55,200 --> 00:15:57,650
It seems like you have
dealt with Ming Xin swiftly.

230
00:16:03,270 --> 00:16:04,420
It is unscathed.

231
00:16:08,630 --> 00:16:09,870
To revive your companion beast,

232
00:16:10,080 --> 00:16:12,320
you need to resonate with
it using your spiritual veins.

233
00:16:17,080 --> 00:16:18,130
It will be painful.

234
00:16:18,480 --> 00:16:19,520
Let me stay here with you.

235
00:17:04,440 --> 00:17:05,960
The black lingzhi mushroom is working.

236
00:17:06,640 --> 00:17:08,380
If I nurture it for a while,

237
00:17:09,790 --> 00:17:11,290
Twenty-Seven will return.

238
00:17:12,640 --> 00:17:13,730
I finally did it.

239
00:17:35,240 --> 00:17:36,240
What?

240
00:17:36,590 --> 00:17:37,620
Won't you ask

241
00:17:39,350 --> 00:17:40,700
what I did to Ming Xin?

242
00:17:41,590 --> 00:17:42,976
After all, he was going to be

243
00:17:43,000 --> 00:17:44,570
the crown prince of Yaoguang Mountain.

244
00:17:44,920 --> 00:17:45,920
If I hurt him,

245
00:17:46,590 --> 00:17:48,330
Jixing Abyss might be in trouble.

246
00:17:48,640 --> 00:17:49,640
In trouble?

247
00:17:50,640 --> 00:17:51,766
As in neither of us

248
00:17:51,790 --> 00:17:53,090
can handle the consequences?

249
00:17:53,440 --> 00:17:55,330
If you kill him, I'll bring you the blade.

250
00:17:55,920 --> 00:17:57,560
If you spare him, I'll cover your tracks.

251
00:17:58,030 --> 00:17:59,660
I have the Warrior Goddess with me.

252
00:17:59,830 --> 00:18:01,190
What else is there to worry about?

253
00:18:03,640 --> 00:18:04,900
I got the Recording Mirror,

254
00:18:06,270 --> 00:18:07,700
but I spared Ming Xin.

255
00:18:08,160 --> 00:18:10,290
He's going to reveal
my identity to my father.

256
00:18:13,110 --> 00:18:14,110
And you

257
00:18:14,680 --> 00:18:16,140
already have a plan?

258
00:18:18,310 --> 00:18:19,310
Yes.

259
00:18:19,590 --> 00:18:20,590
But

260
00:18:21,110 --> 00:18:22,700
there's one important thing.

261
00:18:23,480 --> 00:18:24,730
I need to check with you.

262
00:18:26,270 --> 00:18:28,276
When did you give me
the Golden Millet Dream?

263
00:18:28,300 --> 00:18:32,060
♪ Maybe I'm just your firefly ♪

264
00:18:34,660 --> 00:18:38,620
♪ That's why I'm so fragile... ♪

265
00:18:39,240 --> 00:18:40,176
Didn't you see me

266
00:18:40,200 --> 00:18:41,530
destroy the Golden Millet Dream?

267
00:18:42,070 --> 00:18:43,510
How could I possibly give it to you?

268
00:18:44,480 --> 00:18:46,380
I undid the seal on Bo's Medical Classics.

269
00:18:48,790 --> 00:18:49,790
The Golden Millet Dream

270
00:18:49,880 --> 00:18:52,220
is the only cure for the Heavenly Grief.

271
00:18:52,350 --> 00:18:53,530
You gave it to me.

272
00:18:55,480 --> 00:18:56,616
Like I said,

273
00:18:56,640 --> 00:18:57,640
I did not.

274
00:18:57,960 --> 00:19:00,290
In Zhangwei Mountain,
you asked if I was Ming Xian.

275
00:19:01,550 --> 00:19:03,750
You said you'd only ask me
that question one last time.

276
00:19:05,110 --> 00:19:06,110
So today,

277
00:19:07,030 --> 00:19:08,430
I'm asking you again one last time.

278
00:19:08,640 --> 00:19:09,920
If you won't answer my question,

279
00:19:10,830 --> 00:19:11,830
I will not ask it again.

280
00:19:12,220 --> 00:19:15,420
♪ My faint light ♪

281
00:19:15,460 --> 00:19:20,300
♪ Will shine through for your brilliance ♪

282
00:19:20,660 --> 00:19:26,300
♪ If your world was once
an endless wasteland ♪

283
00:19:27,060 --> 00:19:32,700
♪ I'd tear myself apart to
fill the wounds inside you ♪

284
00:19:33,460 --> 00:19:37,860
♪ Even if this life is like a shooting star ♪

285
00:19:37,900 --> 00:19:41,100
♪ Brief only for the
sake of meeting you... ♪

286
00:19:43,960 --> 00:19:46,530
Did you enjoy the scallion pancake?

287
00:20:04,720 --> 00:20:06,800
You brought a scallion
pancake to Zhangwei Mountain?

288
00:20:07,070 --> 00:20:08,070
Is it weird?

289
00:20:08,400 --> 00:20:09,570
I came here for you anyway.

290
00:20:12,030 --> 00:20:13,030
Thank you.

291
00:20:18,750 --> 00:20:20,460
I only realized now

292
00:20:20,640 --> 00:20:21,940
that you're more important to me

293
00:20:23,110 --> 00:20:24,980
than I imagined.

294
00:20:27,550 --> 00:20:28,900
Don't spill anything.

295
00:20:29,550 --> 00:20:31,090
Come. Eat it.

296
00:20:31,900 --> 00:20:34,980
♪ The fireflies fill the night sky... ♪

297
00:20:36,160 --> 00:20:37,160
See?

298
00:20:37,240 --> 00:20:38,246
I'd hate to see you

299
00:20:38,270 --> 00:20:39,900
look at me like that.

300
00:20:40,880 --> 00:20:42,240
I gave you the Golden Millet Dream

301
00:20:42,350 --> 00:20:43,380
for one purpose only,

302
00:20:43,830 --> 00:20:45,290
so that you can live.

303
00:20:47,880 --> 00:20:49,440
I don't want you to feel indebted to me

304
00:20:50,440 --> 00:20:52,200
or that you need to do
anything to repay me.

305
00:20:56,620 --> 00:21:01,020
♪ Even in this restless world ♪

306
00:21:01,060 --> 00:21:04,180
♪ My faint light ♪

307
00:21:04,340 --> 00:21:09,140
♪ Will shine through for your brilliance ♪

308
00:21:09,500 --> 00:21:14,856
♪ If your world was once
an endless wasteland... ♪

309
00:21:14,880 --> 00:21:16,530
You ought to know me better.

310
00:21:17,110 --> 00:21:18,006
I'm a prideful woman.

311
00:21:18,030 --> 00:21:21,490
I will never fall for someone
out of indebtedness.

312
00:21:23,750 --> 00:21:26,420
Yes. You and your pride.

313
00:21:27,030 --> 00:21:28,030
You're invincible.

314
00:21:29,980 --> 00:21:34,180
♪ In this fleeting life ♪

315
00:21:35,020 --> 00:21:42,820
♪ I'll still be your light ♪

316
00:22:18,750 --> 00:22:20,750
Ji Bozai.
(Watch on www.kisskh.ca to support Admin)

317
00:22:22,590 --> 00:22:23,590
Ming Xian.

318
00:22:25,160 --> 00:22:27,700
You two trespassed into Yaoguang Palace

319
00:22:27,920 --> 00:22:29,090
to kidnap me.

320
00:22:29,830 --> 00:22:30,490
What?

321
00:22:30,830 --> 00:22:32,620
Are you betraying Yaoguang Mountain

322
00:22:32,790 --> 00:22:34,140
and siding with Jixing Abyss now?

323
00:22:39,000 --> 00:22:40,000
Looking for something?

324
00:22:41,830 --> 00:22:43,940
Oh, this thing from the Emperor

325
00:22:44,960 --> 00:22:45,960
of Zhushui?

326
00:22:47,110 --> 00:22:48,110
What do you want?

327
00:22:50,110 --> 00:22:51,180
Easy.

328
00:22:51,720 --> 00:22:52,720
It won't be for long.

329
00:22:55,720 --> 00:22:57,096
I can finally

330
00:22:57,120 --> 00:22:59,220
use this Soul-seizing Technique on you.

331
00:22:59,960 --> 00:23:00,960
Are you ready?

332
00:23:10,400 --> 00:23:11,400
Speak.

333
00:23:11,830 --> 00:23:13,700
The Emperor of Zhushui gave you power

334
00:23:13,920 --> 00:23:15,530
and even the compass.

335
00:23:16,000 --> 00:23:17,570
What did he tell you to do?

336
00:23:18,790 --> 00:23:19,790
Ming Xian.

337
00:23:20,200 --> 00:23:22,050
Do you think you can be the crown prince

338
00:23:22,480 --> 00:23:24,660
just because you have the Recording Mirror?

339
00:23:24,920 --> 00:23:26,250
Dream on!

340
00:23:27,310 --> 00:23:29,530
You will not steal my thunder again!

341
00:23:30,720 --> 00:23:31,720
Ming Xian.

342
00:23:31,830 --> 00:23:35,140
Only I can be the crown prince.

343
00:23:40,030 --> 00:23:41,860
So his greatest fear

344
00:23:42,640 --> 00:23:43,810
is you?

345
00:23:45,270 --> 00:23:47,420
That's my loser of a brother for you.

346
00:23:47,590 --> 00:23:48,590
Don't mind him.

347
00:23:49,750 --> 00:23:52,490
Smiling? You have no right to be smug.

348
00:23:53,480 --> 00:23:55,250
What did the Emperor tell me to do?

349
00:23:55,920 --> 00:23:57,420
Listen carefully.

350
00:23:57,960 --> 00:24:01,460
He told me to capture you alive and
bring you to Zhushui Spiritual State.

351
00:24:02,160 --> 00:24:03,570
You're an outsider.

352
00:24:04,110 --> 00:24:04,976
You don't carry

353
00:24:05,000 --> 00:24:07,220
the bloodline of Yaoguang Palace.

354
00:24:07,510 --> 00:24:08,510
You

355
00:24:08,720 --> 00:24:10,940
are a descendant of the Bo clan!

356
00:24:19,160 --> 00:24:20,160
What did you say?

357
00:24:21,590 --> 00:24:23,530
The elders in Yaoguang Palace claimed

358
00:24:23,920 --> 00:24:27,460
that two wandering physicians once
sojourned in Yaoguang Mountain.

359
00:24:27,790 --> 00:24:28,790
One of them

360
00:24:29,000 --> 00:24:31,940
fell in love and had a child
with one of the local warriors.

361
00:24:32,510 --> 00:24:33,510
Can you guess

362
00:24:33,640 --> 00:24:35,490
if it's you?

363
00:24:36,200 --> 00:24:37,940
The Emperor of Zhushui also said

364
00:24:38,270 --> 00:24:40,150
that since you could
enter the Zhulong Barrier,

365
00:24:40,400 --> 00:24:43,770
it meant you were the
descendant of the Bo clan.

366
00:24:49,310 --> 00:24:51,180
Father. Mother.

367
00:24:51,310 --> 00:24:52,310
Look.

368
00:24:52,350 --> 00:24:58,090
The crown prince of Yaoguang
Mountain can only be me!

369
00:25:02,000 --> 00:25:03,800
Let me find out the
truth in Yaoguang Palace.

370
00:25:04,480 --> 00:25:05,480
Ming Yi.

371
00:25:17,200 --> 00:25:18,490
Father has found out.

372
00:25:18,680 --> 00:25:19,700
He has erected a barrier

373
00:25:20,920 --> 00:25:22,020
so that I cannot return.

374
00:25:38,790 --> 00:25:39,860
The barrier is now broken.

375
00:25:40,640 --> 00:25:41,810
Guards will arrive soon.

376
00:25:42,110 --> 00:25:44,090
Don't worry. I'll stand guard.

377
00:25:44,550 --> 00:25:45,700
No one will bother you.

378
00:25:47,270 --> 00:25:48,270
Ming Yi.

379
00:25:51,175 --> 00:26:11,175
Officail Website : dramacool.club  Translate by =Qari= @Team Viki

380
00:25:53,200 --> 00:25:54,200
I can handle it.

381
00:26:28,000 --> 00:26:29,000
You...

382
00:26:29,830 --> 00:26:31,220
How did you come back?

383
00:26:31,960 --> 00:26:33,460
How could they do this to you?

384
00:26:33,920 --> 00:26:36,140
They know you're a fairy.

385
00:26:36,240 --> 00:26:38,440
So they agreed to appoint
Ming Xin as the crown prince.

386
00:26:38,510 --> 00:26:39,670
You shouldn't have come back.

387
00:26:41,350 --> 00:26:42,750
I'll take you away from this place.

388
00:26:44,000 --> 00:26:45,570
Your father thinks you're a traitor.

389
00:26:45,720 --> 00:26:47,856
Even you can't be sure that
you can get out of this place

390
00:26:47,880 --> 00:26:48,806
alive.

391
00:26:48,830 --> 00:26:50,046
And you want me to come with you?

392
00:26:50,070 --> 00:26:51,330
Do you think you can escape?

393
00:26:51,640 --> 00:26:53,050
Master told me

394
00:26:53,350 --> 00:26:55,620
that you were safe in Yaoguang Palace.

395
00:26:56,350 --> 00:26:57,416
Look at you now.

396
00:26:57,440 --> 00:26:58,806
I will bring you to safety even if it means

397
00:26:58,830 --> 00:27:00,190
everyone will view me as an enemy.

398
00:27:06,720 --> 00:27:07,720
Just go.

399
00:27:07,920 --> 00:27:09,250
I will not leave with you.

400
00:27:14,510 --> 00:27:15,980
Your Majesty, you won't come with me

401
00:27:16,480 --> 00:27:20,010
because you don't think
I can bring you to safety

402
00:27:23,160 --> 00:27:24,160
or because.

403
00:27:27,310 --> 00:27:29,380
I am not your daughter?

404
00:27:35,240 --> 00:27:36,250
What did you say?

405
00:27:37,350 --> 00:27:40,140
Ming Xin was given the
task of taking me back alive

406
00:27:40,200 --> 00:27:41,660
by the Emperor of Zhushui

407
00:27:42,590 --> 00:27:44,770
because the Emperor found out

408
00:27:46,480 --> 00:27:49,730
that I do not carry the
bloodline of Yaoguang Palace.

409
00:27:50,110 --> 00:27:51,790
He said I was a descendant of the Bo clan.

410
00:27:53,790 --> 00:27:55,810
No wonder you never called me Mother

411
00:27:56,270 --> 00:27:58,220
after you barged into this place.

412
00:28:24,310 --> 00:28:25,310
Master She.

413
00:28:30,960 --> 00:28:32,460
Ming Yi wrote to me,

414
00:28:33,200 --> 00:28:35,440
telling me that you gave the
Golden Millet Dream to her.

415
00:28:48,480 --> 00:28:50,980
I've never thanked anyone in my life.

416
00:28:51,830 --> 00:28:53,150
But I'll make an exception today.

417
00:28:54,920 --> 00:28:55,920
Stand upright.

418
00:28:56,960 --> 00:28:57,960
Stand upright.

419
00:29:01,720 --> 00:29:02,720
Master She.

420
00:29:04,640 --> 00:29:05,640
Do not return the bow.

421
00:29:06,030 --> 00:29:07,030
Rest assured.

422
00:29:07,310 --> 00:29:08,806
I will repay the favor.

423
00:29:08,830 --> 00:29:10,726
I will find the Diwu tree's
core as soon as possible

424
00:29:10,750 --> 00:29:12,490
and make the Golden Millet Dream for you.

425
00:29:13,640 --> 00:29:16,460
Thank you, Master She.

426
00:29:16,880 --> 00:29:17,880
No need.

427
00:29:21,960 --> 00:29:24,856
Ming Yi also mentioned

428
00:29:24,880 --> 00:29:27,176
that Ming Xin accused
her of being a descendant

429
00:29:27,200 --> 00:29:28,660
of the Bo clan.

430
00:29:28,960 --> 00:29:29,960
Did that happen?

431
00:29:32,960 --> 00:29:34,140
What else did Ming Xin say?

432
00:29:37,400 --> 00:29:38,400
Tell us.

433
00:29:38,640 --> 00:29:41,050
So where did the
wandering Bo physicians go?

434
00:29:41,200 --> 00:29:43,660
I was told one died
from labor complications.

435
00:29:43,830 --> 00:29:46,380
And the other one was last seen

436
00:29:46,720 --> 00:29:48,730
leaving Yaoguang Palace

437
00:29:49,030 --> 00:29:50,420
with a newborn baby.

438
00:29:55,350 --> 00:29:56,620
You returned

439
00:29:57,830 --> 00:29:59,770
to find the truth.

440
00:30:01,680 --> 00:30:03,980
If I tell you the truth,

441
00:30:05,270 --> 00:30:07,460
will you stop pestering me?

442
00:30:12,480 --> 00:30:13,770
Have you ever wondered

443
00:30:15,000 --> 00:30:16,090
why I have treated you so

444
00:30:17,440 --> 00:30:19,010
ever since you were little?

445
00:30:20,240 --> 00:30:21,460
You are smart.

446
00:30:22,110 --> 00:30:24,330
You won every Qingyun Tournament.

447
00:30:25,590 --> 00:30:27,220
You wouldn't even dare

448
00:30:28,440 --> 00:30:30,140
to make a mistake or lose

449
00:30:30,920 --> 00:30:32,010
in your training.

450
00:30:33,960 --> 00:30:35,696
But I never cared

451
00:30:35,720 --> 00:30:37,420
what you wanted,

452
00:30:38,400 --> 00:30:40,420
or if you were hurt

453
00:30:41,110 --> 00:30:42,110
or hungry.

454
00:30:43,440 --> 00:30:44,896
No mother would ever

455
00:30:44,920 --> 00:30:46,660
treat her child like this.

456
00:30:50,440 --> 00:30:51,730
Given your intelligence,

457
00:30:53,310 --> 00:30:57,330
I thought you'd have guessed it.

458
00:30:58,480 --> 00:31:00,140
So...

459
00:31:02,550 --> 00:31:03,980
So who am I?

460
00:31:05,680 --> 00:31:07,160
Your father, the Emperor of Yaoguang,

461
00:31:07,830 --> 00:31:11,050
and I do not love each other.

462
00:31:12,030 --> 00:31:13,940
He took Madam Meng
in as his consort one day

463
00:31:14,240 --> 00:31:15,730
and showered her with affection.

464
00:31:17,110 --> 00:31:18,900
Everyone in Yaoguang Palace said

465
00:31:19,270 --> 00:31:20,656
that when Madam Meng gave birth

466
00:31:20,680 --> 00:31:22,180
to a son with spiritual veins,

467
00:31:22,350 --> 00:31:23,730
she would replace me

468
00:31:24,480 --> 00:31:26,620
as the Empress of Yaoguang.

469
00:31:28,160 --> 00:31:28,980
Therefore,

470
00:31:29,030 --> 00:31:30,660
I must give birth to a son

471
00:31:31,310 --> 00:31:34,460
with spiritual veins before she does.

472
00:31:36,660 --> 00:31:37,936
[20 Years Ago]

473
00:31:37,960 --> 00:31:38,960
There, there.

474
00:31:40,160 --> 00:31:40,617
Good boy.

475
00:31:40,641 --> 00:31:42,810
Baby. My baby.

476
00:31:43,400 --> 00:31:44,400
Quick.

477
00:31:44,830 --> 00:31:46,380
Bring me my baby.

478
00:31:48,830 --> 00:31:49,980
My baby.

479
00:32:01,830 --> 00:32:04,250
Impossible. This can't be right.

480
00:32:05,160 --> 00:32:08,010
My son must have spiritual veins.

481
00:32:09,340 --> 00:32:10,896
Who would have thought - Impossible!

482
00:32:10,920 --> 00:32:11,727
This is impossible!

483
00:32:11,751 --> 00:32:15,250
The son whom I toiled so much to conceive

484
00:32:17,200 --> 00:32:19,250
was born without spiritual veins?

485
00:32:21,550 --> 00:32:24,290
Without spiritual veins?

486
00:32:25,400 --> 00:32:27,700
Yes. The irony of it.

487
00:32:29,830 --> 00:32:33,140
God took pity on me and gave me a son.

488
00:32:34,750 --> 00:32:36,330
But in everyone's eyes,

489
00:32:37,510 --> 00:32:40,176
he's just a useless person
with no spiritual veins.

490
00:32:40,200 --> 00:32:42,050
He can never be a crown prince.

491
00:32:42,200 --> 00:32:44,090
He won't even be able to survive.

492
00:32:44,590 --> 00:32:45,590
So.

493
00:32:47,510 --> 00:32:48,730
Who am I?

494
00:32:49,590 --> 00:32:51,086
The serendipitous but hapless victim

495
00:32:51,110 --> 00:32:52,770
of this tragedy.

496
00:32:54,200 --> 00:32:55,220
Coincidentally,

497
00:32:55,640 --> 00:32:57,180
another baby was born

498
00:32:58,070 --> 00:33:00,570
at the same time in Yaoguang Palace.

499
00:33:01,240 --> 00:33:03,290
It was a baby girl

500
00:33:03,480 --> 00:33:06,570
yet she was born with
strong spiritual veins.

501
00:33:07,400 --> 00:33:09,730
So I made the decision.

502
00:33:10,550 --> 00:33:12,330
To save my son,

503
00:33:12,830 --> 00:33:15,006
I took you, who were born
on the same day, away

504
00:33:15,030 --> 00:33:16,530
to replace my son.

505
00:33:17,640 --> 00:33:20,700
Your Majesty, I'm begging you.

506
00:33:21,550 --> 00:33:23,086
Yucen is already dead.

507
00:33:23,110 --> 00:33:24,940
This is her only child.

508
00:33:29,200 --> 00:33:31,660
Bo Yulan, you know very well

509
00:33:32,110 --> 00:33:35,530
why your sister died
from birth complications.

510
00:33:36,030 --> 00:33:38,380
She was hunted down
by Zhushui Spiritual State

511
00:33:38,790 --> 00:33:40,380
and was gravely injured.

512
00:33:40,750 --> 00:33:42,900
She was too weak to carry a baby,

513
00:33:43,310 --> 00:33:45,220
yet she risked everything
to deliver her baby

514
00:33:45,830 --> 00:33:48,010
for the sake of love.

515
00:33:48,440 --> 00:33:49,570
And her lover

516
00:33:49,830 --> 00:33:52,050
couldn't do anything to protect her baby.

517
00:33:52,750 --> 00:33:54,900
He is a warrior

518
00:33:55,640 --> 00:33:57,460
but he consummated with a foreign fairy.

519
00:33:57,790 --> 00:33:59,570
He is now imprisoned.

520
00:34:01,830 --> 00:34:03,530
I felt bad for Yucen,

521
00:34:03,680 --> 00:34:05,980
so I snuck her into the
palace for her delivery.

522
00:34:07,160 --> 00:34:10,340
Now that Yucen is gone,

523
00:34:11,280 --> 00:34:14,300
do you think you can protect the baby?

524
00:34:50,960 --> 00:34:53,460
This baby was born with unrivaled

525
00:34:53,760 --> 00:34:55,090
spiritual veins and potentials.

526
00:34:55,670 --> 00:34:59,820
She is destined to rise above all.

527
00:35:01,630 --> 00:35:02,630
I know

528
00:35:03,190 --> 00:35:06,170
your clan has something
called the Veil of Illusion

529
00:35:06,670 --> 00:35:08,300
that can conceal her gender.

530
00:35:09,030 --> 00:35:10,086
You and your sister

531
00:35:10,110 --> 00:35:11,936
used that technique to evade the manhunt

532
00:35:11,960 --> 00:35:13,610
in Zhushui Spiritual State.

533
00:35:14,030 --> 00:35:15,940
Tell me how to use the technique

534
00:35:16,320 --> 00:35:18,170
and I'll release your sister's lover.

535
00:35:19,360 --> 00:35:20,690
This baby

536
00:35:22,230 --> 00:35:26,900
will be the respected crown
prince of Yaoguang Mountain.

537
00:35:27,510 --> 00:35:32,650
I will make her the ruler of Six Realms.

538
00:35:45,960 --> 00:35:46,960
So,

539
00:35:48,670 --> 00:35:50,380
I really am...

540
00:35:52,280 --> 00:35:55,900
Yes, the daughter of Bo Yucen,

541
00:35:56,320 --> 00:35:58,940
the descendant of the Bo clan.

542
00:36:05,360 --> 00:36:07,420
Then, my father is...?

543
00:36:23,630 --> 00:36:24,630
Master She.

544
00:36:25,960 --> 00:36:26,960
I heard

545
00:36:28,480 --> 00:36:31,000
that the ancestors of the Bo
clan would leave behind portraits.

546
00:36:32,110 --> 00:36:34,070
As long as someone pays
respect to the portraits,

547
00:36:34,150 --> 00:36:35,260
their divine consciousness

548
00:36:35,710 --> 00:36:38,980
will remain in the Bo
clan's ancestral home.

549
00:36:40,800 --> 00:36:42,170
That day, in Zhangwei Mountain,

550
00:36:43,230 --> 00:36:44,230
Ming Yi

551
00:36:45,670 --> 00:36:47,650
saw another fairy from the Bo clan,

552
00:36:51,030 --> 00:36:52,030
Bo Yucen.

553
00:36:55,710 --> 00:36:56,780
She saw Yucen?

554
00:36:58,190 --> 00:36:59,420
She truly saw Yucen?

555
00:37:00,510 --> 00:37:01,820
So, you do know Bo Yucen.

556
00:37:08,230 --> 00:37:09,490
Fairy Bo Yucen

557
00:37:10,880 --> 00:37:14,610
said something weird to Ming Yi.

558
00:37:19,550 --> 00:37:20,550
What did she say?

559
00:37:22,760 --> 00:37:25,650
The Bo clan still has one
descendant in this world.

560
00:37:26,360 --> 00:37:27,740
And that's my child.

561
00:37:28,920 --> 00:37:29,920
But I hope

562
00:37:30,360 --> 00:37:31,646
no one will ever find out

563
00:37:31,670 --> 00:37:33,210
about her identity

564
00:37:33,920 --> 00:37:36,860
or whereabouts.

565
00:37:42,510 --> 00:37:43,610
Oh, my baby.

566
00:37:45,110 --> 00:37:46,530
Never have I ever imagined

567
00:37:48,000 --> 00:37:50,570
that I would be able to see you again.

568
00:37:53,000 --> 00:37:54,000
Ming Yi

569
00:37:55,030 --> 00:37:56,940
didn't know what she meant.

570
00:38:01,360 --> 00:38:02,360
But...

571
00:38:04,920 --> 00:38:06,420
Master She, you must know.

572
00:38:10,550 --> 00:38:11,550
I thought

573
00:38:12,320 --> 00:38:13,780
that if Ming Yi could meet her,

574
00:38:14,840 --> 00:38:17,120
it means someone is still
paying respect to her portrait.

575
00:38:19,800 --> 00:38:20,940
Is that you, Master She?

576
00:38:32,440 --> 00:38:33,440
Master She,

577
00:38:34,480 --> 00:38:35,480
I admit

578
00:38:36,000 --> 00:38:38,440
that I once asked my companion
beast to dig around your past.

579
00:38:39,190 --> 00:38:42,490
Ming Xian became a warrior of
Yaoguang Mountain at the age of 13.

580
00:38:43,320 --> 00:38:44,320
And you

581
00:38:44,760 --> 00:38:46,260
suddenly did everything you could

582
00:38:46,840 --> 00:38:49,260
to be the venerable for
Yaoguang Mountain's warrior ranks.

583
00:38:50,400 --> 00:38:51,400
That's because

584
00:38:53,320 --> 00:38:56,170
you want to tutor the
crown prince, Ming Xian.

585
00:39:00,960 --> 00:39:01,960
Well done!

586
00:39:03,960 --> 00:39:04,960
Greetings, Venerable.

587
00:39:05,440 --> 00:39:06,440
Your Highness.

588
00:39:06,760 --> 00:39:08,170
No need to bow to me, Venerable.

589
00:39:08,710 --> 00:39:10,300
I am now one of the warriors.

590
00:39:10,760 --> 00:39:13,780
I should bow to you instead.

591
00:39:15,280 --> 00:39:16,280
Your Highness,

592
00:39:16,800 --> 00:39:18,530
your form was excellent just now.

593
00:39:18,840 --> 00:39:21,340
Perhaps you shouldn't call me Venerable.

594
00:39:21,480 --> 00:39:22,480
Let me be your master.

595
00:39:22,630 --> 00:39:23,980
I'll take you in as my disciple.

596
00:39:24,960 --> 00:39:25,960
You?

597
00:39:27,320 --> 00:39:28,780
Why should I be your disciple?

598
00:39:30,070 --> 00:39:31,090
What can you teach me?

599
00:39:32,800 --> 00:39:33,820
Prideful, aren't you?

600
00:39:34,320 --> 00:39:35,530
Let's have a match then.

601
00:39:35,960 --> 00:39:37,050
If I win,

602
00:39:37,400 --> 00:39:38,690
you'll have to call me Master.

603
00:39:39,760 --> 00:39:40,760
Sure.

604
00:39:46,280 --> 00:39:47,376
After Ming Xin

605
00:39:47,400 --> 00:39:48,980
confessed,

606
00:39:50,030 --> 00:39:51,530
you began to suspect me, didn't you?

607
00:39:52,360 --> 00:39:53,610
I didn't mean to offend you.

608
00:39:54,710 --> 00:39:55,980
All I'm after is the truth.

609
00:39:57,280 --> 00:40:00,490
Will you tell me the truth, Master She?

610
00:40:02,760 --> 00:40:04,460
Were you in love

611
00:40:07,110 --> 00:40:08,300
with Fairy Bo Yucen?

612
00:40:12,880 --> 00:40:14,490
Your father

613
00:40:14,840 --> 00:40:16,420
was the warrior

614
00:40:16,670 --> 00:40:20,130
of Yaoguang Mountain, She Tianlin.

615
00:40:32,030 --> 00:40:36,530
So in the Bo clan's ancestral home, I met

616
00:40:37,400 --> 00:40:40,050
my mother.

617
00:40:41,760 --> 00:40:43,980
The one I've known since I was little,

618
00:40:45,920 --> 00:40:47,006
the one who has been staying by my side,

619
00:40:47,030 --> 00:40:49,170
the one whom I call Master is...

620
00:41:09,480 --> 00:41:10,490
So Ming Yi

621
00:41:12,150 --> 00:41:14,340
is your child with Fairy Bo Yucen.

622
00:41:27,590 --> 00:41:29,010
When Yucen went into labor,

623
00:41:30,360 --> 00:41:31,936
I was imprisoned by the Empress.

624
00:41:31,960 --> 00:41:33,490
When I was released,

625
00:41:33,550 --> 00:41:34,550
Yucen had already passed

626
00:41:37,110 --> 00:41:38,980
from birth complications.

627
00:41:41,760 --> 00:41:45,170
I couldn't even look at her one last time.

628
00:41:53,110 --> 00:41:54,110
By then,

629
00:41:55,760 --> 00:41:56,760
your daughter

630
00:41:58,070 --> 00:42:00,460
had already become the son of the Empress.

631
00:42:01,960 --> 00:42:03,210
I was at my wits' end.

632
00:42:03,800 --> 00:42:05,090
I had no other option.

633
00:42:06,030 --> 00:42:07,030
What can I do?

634
00:42:07,710 --> 00:42:09,650
I was just an ordinary warrior

635
00:42:09,710 --> 00:42:11,296
and they were the entire Yaoguang Palace.

636
00:42:11,320 --> 00:42:14,046
Could I fight them all?

637
00:42:14,070 --> 00:42:15,610
Could I fight the Empress?

638
00:42:18,400 --> 00:42:19,680
I could only endure it silently.

639
00:42:22,480 --> 00:42:23,860
Yucen's portrait

640
00:42:25,280 --> 00:42:28,090
contains our shared memories.

641
00:42:30,320 --> 00:42:32,050
For 21 years,

642
00:42:33,840 --> 00:42:35,860
for all 21 years,

643
00:42:38,280 --> 00:42:41,380
those cherished past memories,

644
00:42:42,800 --> 00:42:44,526
and Ming Yi's future

645
00:42:44,550 --> 00:42:48,650
have kept me alive.

646
00:42:51,320 --> 00:42:52,900
For 21 years,

647
00:42:55,230 --> 00:42:56,980
have you never intended

648
00:42:57,710 --> 00:42:59,420
to tell Ming Yi the truth?

649
00:43:00,760 --> 00:43:02,210
You would rather Ming Yi live

650
00:43:03,960 --> 00:43:06,380
in deception forever?

651
00:43:35,100 --> 00:43:38,300
♪ When the drifting clouds ♪

652
00:43:38,380 --> 00:43:40,700
♪ Flow toward me ♪

653
00:43:42,140 --> 00:43:44,940
♪ They drench my very soul ♪

654
00:43:44,980 --> 00:43:47,300
♪ Until it turns weak ♪

655
00:43:49,220 --> 00:43:51,980
♪ I deceive myself into
thinking that to love once ♪

656
00:43:52,020 --> 00:43:54,340
♪ Is enough ♪

657
00:43:55,660 --> 00:44:00,900
♪ Even if no true vow has ever been given ♪

658
00:44:02,740 --> 00:44:09,620
♪ From the stars, how long must
my tears travel to reach your heart? ♪

659
00:44:09,900 --> 00:44:16,220
♪ The tenderness you give me
is but love's poisonous wine ♪

660
00:44:17,180 --> 00:44:19,780
♪ I drink down all of my sorrow ♪

661
00:44:20,500 --> 00:44:23,780
♪ To trade for your freedom ♪

662
00:44:24,020 --> 00:44:29,740
♪ Once I've tasted love, I
long to be lost in its wine ♪

663
00:44:30,860 --> 00:44:37,540
♪ After long struggles in the
abyss, I ask the heavens ♪

664
00:44:37,940 --> 00:44:44,620
♪ Even if my armor shatters
for you, what does it matter? ♪

665
00:44:45,100 --> 00:44:48,380
♪ Fate is never wrong ♪

666
00:44:48,460 --> 00:44:51,860
♪ Even the sun must one day fall ♪

667
00:44:52,340 --> 00:44:59,180
♪ Against the world's absurdity,
I fight with all my might ♪

668
00:45:02,940 --> 00:45:09,756
♪ From the stars, how long must
my tears travel to reach your heart? ♪

669
00:45:09,780 --> 00:45:16,020
♪ The tenderness you give me
is but love's poisonous wine ♪

670
00:45:16,900 --> 00:45:19,500
♪ I drink down all of my sorrow ♪

671
00:45:20,260 --> 00:45:23,500
♪ To trade for your freedom ♪

672
00:45:23,740 --> 00:45:30,540
♪ Once I've tasted love, I
long to be lost in its wine ♪
